_comment: Most links to server JARs came from https://mcversions.net/

vanilla.description: The base game of Minecraft with no extra features or modifications.

bukkit.description: An extension of vanilla which adds support for server-side modding and plugins.

spigot.description: A fork of Bukkit which improves performance and fixes bugs ahead of time (Recommended).

forge.description: A highly popular mod API for Minecraft which allows you to add new content to the game.
